{"data":{"page":{"id":"d7a4767b-75be-5b53-ab92-8f57ec3348fc","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/innovaconst\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived website</a>\n</p>\n<p>Grupo InnovaConst asked us (Webmarket) to create a Flash website to promote their services online. It was a straightforward project without CMS. Just a few pages with animated transitions and eye-catching imagery.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/64f38977f8bec9b6aabc0a87f82cf568/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/64f38977f8bec9b6aabc0a87f82cf568/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/64f38977f8bec9b6aabc0a87f82cf568/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>","fields":{"prefix":"16 June 2007"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Grupo innovaconst","cover":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/grupo-innovaconst/","source":"work"}}